description: Project setup and dev environment rules
globs:
  - "**/*"
alwaysApply: true
---

- Use TypeScript in strict mode.
- Project uses Next.js with App Router (not Pages Router).
- Structure all components by feature (`/components/map/`, `/components/trip/`, etc).
- Store environment variables in `.env.local` using the `.env.example` template.
- Run project locally with:
  ```bash
  npm install && npm run dev
  ```
